<p>
    <b>Passion to Action</b> (P2A) is a statewide youth-led advisory board to Washington State’s Children’s Administration (CA).
    CA understands the importance of partnering with our youth in the work we do. P2A members provide CA with input,
    feedback and recommendations regarding the agency’s policies, practices and publications. Additionally, CA utilizes
    P2A members in many of the agency’s training courses and presentations to ensure that caseworkers, foster parents and
    the community at large learn about the experience of being in the foster care system from those who have the expertise,
    youth in care and alumni.
</p>

